title: Kyle Sandilands looks at Imogen Anthony's Maxim shoot | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share The couple were out to lunch with a group of friends, and Imogen sat next to Kyle in a raunchy outfit as he admired her latest work. It is not the first time Imogen has graced the cover of the magazine as she previously modelled for Maxim in early 2014. Her biggest fan! The 45-year-old appeared a little shocked - but also very impressed - as he scanned the pages of the Australian men's magazine She's back! It is not the first time Imogen has graced the cover of the magazine as she previously modelled for Maxim in early 2014 For the outing, Kyle dressed in his trademark ensemble, that featured a plain black shirt and dark pants. Meanwhile, Imogen cut a much more colourful figure, looking sensational in one of her bold outfits. The stylish star, who is known for being fashion forward, beat the heat in a blank tank top and denim cutoffs. She wore fishnet stockings and a pair of knee-high boots that featured a zebra pattern. High-profile couple: The loved-up pair were out to lunch in Sydney's Double Bay The stunner covered up in a paperboy hat and a pair of reflective shades, leaving her blonde locks out for the lunch date.
